{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"1254","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":null,"news_on_top":"1","news_title":"全國首座綠電車站 台鐵台東站 年減碳82萬公斤","news_summary":null,"image_path":null,"news_des":"","news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%8F%B0%E6%9D%B1%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99.jpg' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;' /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>台東火車站計程車排班區加裝太陽光電棚架，讓運將及搭車乘客免受日曬雨淋之苦。（記者陳賢義攝）</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr style='box-sizing: content-box; border-radius: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 20px 0px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent); color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;' />\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>2022/08/16 05:30</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-famil